    "title": "あの輝きに愛を込めて",
    "enTitle": "Fill that Shine with Love",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ステイゴールドと\n小旅行に行くことになったある日――",
            "enText": "On a certain day, Stay Gold and I decided to \nembark on a little expedition —",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -7896175709674090633
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -8972750597812227545
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5337039022462714611,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アナウンスの声",
            "enName": "Announcement",
            "jpText": "『急行の待ち合わせのため、\n数分間停車いたします――』",
            "enText": "\"To allow the express train to pass, we \nwill be pausing service for a moment —\"",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 80,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": -1268309782496213640
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": 8992181437526905819
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": 5613749404173397825
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4877167305197867216,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "目的の駅までまだまだ遠い。\n背もたれに寄りかかり、\n窓外を眺めていると――",
            "enText": "Our destination is still many stations away. \nI leaned against the backrest, peeked out \nthe window and —",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 103,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -9137831492471168933
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 6885704917480950443
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 7260272681920272990
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2701074464821995433,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "おっ、ありゃ美味そうな駅弁だな～。",
            "enText": "<i>Ohhh</i>, that boxed lunch looks pretty good～",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "voiceIdx": 31,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "なんか外いる！？",
                    "enText": "Huh?! She's outside?!",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 136,
                    "pathId": -135817573751136011
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 149,
                    "pathId": 5113703722814735058
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3864424173804872841,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "さて！\n……で、どこだろうな～、ここは。",
            "enText": "Now then! …<i>Oh</i>, wonder where we are～",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "voiceIdx": 34,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "それはこっちのセリフだよ",
                    "enText": "Shouldn't I be the one asking that?",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 55,
                    "pathId": 8242042444974049604
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 98,
                    "pathId": -2160439846993308285
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": 6938396036226750634
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6574022073664204885,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "駅を出てしばらく歩くと、\n市街地にたどり着いた。",
            "enText": "After leaving the station, we found \nourselves in the shopping strip.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 76,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": -7431797237541763123
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 87,
                    "pathId": 6291810751615515203
