            "pathId": 3113474089819232807,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "店主のおじさん",
            "enName": "Elderly Storekeeper",
            "jpText": "いらっしゃい……って、あれ！\nもしかしてステイゴールドか！？",
            "enText": "Welcome…… <i>huh!</i> May it be that you're \nStay Gold!?",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": 3952505726273473511
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": -6540339923652353418
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8403119210172463947,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "ん、そうだが？",
            "enText": "<i>Mhm</i>, that's me, and?",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 54,
            "voiceIdx": 20,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 27,
                    "pathId": -5048874389855645525
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 65,
                    "pathId": -6301115426465361092
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2288378414144867960,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "店主のおじさん",
            "enName": "Elderly Storekeeper",
            "jpText": "こりゃ驚いた！　まさか会えるだなんて！\n前にな、アンタの走りを見たことがあんだよ！",
            "enText": "You've surprised this old man! To think \nI'd be granted the chance to meet you! \nI've seen you running in the races!",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 109,
                    "pathId": 1476838348161678129
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 109,
                    "pathId": -3696832890202574983
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1892299037662052883,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "店主のおじさん",
            "enName": "Elderly Storekeeper",
            "jpText": "最後の一瞬まで何が起こるかわからない。\n――そんな走りに心掴まれちゃってよ！",
            "enText": "And your races always keep me on the \nedge of my seat! I can never guess how \nthey'll end when you're there.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -4138582514368613474
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": -19456103809630782
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8070415455223672326,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "店主のおじさん",
            "enName": "Elderly Storekeeper",
            "jpText": "……あ、そうだ！　ちょっと待っててくれ！！",
            "enText": "……<i>Ah</i>, that's right! Please give \nme one moment!!!",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -5560534656514573541
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": 1887774832317462190
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8928338599659681511,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そう言って、店主は店の奥へと向かっていく。",
            "enText": "The storekeeper then dashed into \nthe back of the store.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ここまで君の走りは届いているんだな",
                    "enText": "Seems like you even reached people here",
                    "nextBlock": 15
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "ここまで貴方の走りは届いているんだね",
                    "enText": "Seems like you even reached people here",
                    "nextBlock": 15
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -2215373921825517908
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -5195176922619334425
