            "pathId": 5268965060939621286,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "店主のおじさん",
            "enName": "Elderly Storekeeper",
            "jpText": "俺の応援の証さ！\nいつか渡したいと思って作ってたんだ。",
            "enText": "It's an emblem of my support! I made it \nthinking that it'd be nice if someone got \nto wear it someday.",
