            "pathId": 6870664807652811697,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "……いいデザインだな。\nそうか、手作りか。",
            "enText": "……It's a good design. I see, it's handmade.",
