                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7376022559061956045,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "せっかく降りたのだからと、\n近くの観光地を探していると――",
            "enText": "Since it's not often we get to walk around \nlike this, we decided to look for some \ntouristy spots and —",
