                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": 3611754390365508820
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1558536909002338991,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ふと、ステイゴールドは大きな籠を\n背負ったおばあちゃんに声をかけた。",
            "enText": "Stay Gold suddenly called out to an \nold lady carrying a large basket on \nher back.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 100,
                    "pathId": -5554498984041202902
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 100,
                    "pathId": 8912722711784088820
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6008447573922615166,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "おばあちゃん",
            "enName": "Elderly Lady",
            "jpText": "ええ。裏山でたっくさん採れるのよ。\n今晩はキノコ料理を作ろうと思ってね～。",
            "enText": "Yes yes, I was able to collect plenty of \nthese from the mountainsides. Tonight \nshall be a mushroom feast～",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": 3144625166781890845
                },
