                }
            ],
            "pathId": -329453887924898338,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "おばあちゃん",
            "enName": "Elderly Lady",
            "jpText": "あら、お腹でも空いているのかい？\nもちろん、ウマ娘ならいっぱい食べないとね！",
            "enText": "My my, are you feeling hungry? \nOf course, of course, for you \nhorsegirls need to eat well!",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": -8734925794475376226
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": -2900524037704453323
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": 6872445455964974305
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8312649899716309423,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "本当か、ありがとな！\nなあ、今日はどんなキノコが採れたんだ？\n色々聞かせてくれよ。",
            "enText": "Really? Thank you! Please, I want to \nhear all about the mushrooms you \ngot to pick today.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "voiceIdx": 74,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 8524273679213704902
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 67,
                    "pathId": -7076830143979075577
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 109,
                    "pathId": -5537114420285792822
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8162286923248991282,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ステイゴールドはスタスタと行ってしまった。\nスマホをしまい、急いで彼女を追う。",
            "enText": "Stay Gold picked up the pace and walked \noff with the old lady. I quickly put my \nphone away and chased after her.",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "な、なんて自由な子なんだ……",
                    "enText": "Truly a girl who marches her own pace…",
                    "nextBlock": 28
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "な、なんて自由な子なの……",
                    "enText": "Truly a girl who marches her own pace…",
                    "nextBlock": 28
