        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "そうか？　やってみるといい。\n美味いぞ？",
            "enText": "Really? Thought I'd give it a try. It's \nreally yummy, y'know?",
            "nextBlock": 31,
