            "pathId": 8288045729432150104,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ステイゴールドの真似をして\nお茶漬けで食べてみると――",
            "enText": "Copying Stay Gold, I poured some tea \nover my dish and—",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 80,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
